                <h1>Indiana Background Check Requirements: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>In Indiana, background check requirements vary based on the purpose, such as employment, licensing, or adoption. Generally, employers must obtain written consent from the individual before conducting a check. The state also requires checks through state and national databases, including criminal history, to ensure safety and compliance with regulations.</p>
